category: ANIMALS IN ITALIAN
category comment: 

clue: Don't be afraid--this animal is a pollo

response: a chicken

clue: This animal, gatto, got your lingua?

response: a cat

clue: After all the gelato, I feel as big as a balena, one of these

response: a whale

clue: Tell Leon il cavallo, this animal, has arrived

response: a horse

clue: Farfalle are these creatures, but please don't eat them

response: butterflies

